adMefPerUniPhCurTable.name: adMefPerUniPhCurTable
adMefPerUniPhCurTable.description: This table contains current performance history information that has been recorded since the last 15 minute interval ended and from when the last 1 day interval ended. This table is indexed by ifIndex which SHOULD be maintained in a persistent manner.

adMefPerUniPhCurEntry.description: This specifies the information contained in one entry of the adMefPerUniPhCurTable. It is indexed by an interface's ifIndex.
